snippet.title: FULL 2 HOUR AUDIO Depp vs Heard
snippet.description:
this is the  AUDIO Depp vs Heard in its full length version

0:00 Start of video
2:08 JD says he won't be in a physical altercation
4:07 Toronto 
6:15 JD aks for Toronto tapes
10:50 AH calls JDs actions bratty 
14:41 AH admits she gets angry 
16:38 JD says the fights are often 
18:50 JD brings up Pots and Pans being thrown at him 
19:50 JD mentions cans being thrown at him in Australia 
23:24 Travis fight, AH hit JD 
26:07 AH tells JD he was not punched... he was hit 
28:13 AH gives JD a Xanax 
29:43 AH complains she hasn't been able to fight with JD
32:29 JD says there was a physical altercation on the train on the honeymoon and San Francisco
43:39 Ah complains that JD doesn't do the work 
47:08 AH admits she goes to different bathrooms to find JD 
55:30 AH admits JD needs his meds
56:45 JD praises AH for nice things she does
1:00:05 JD says they are a crime scene waiting to happen 
1:06:40 JD says he put the "monster" away in Australia 
1:08:25 JD says they had 3 physical fights in the last month and a half 
1:11:42 JD asks AH to never lie, she claims she never does 
1:13:40 AH says she worked hard on making the marriage happen 
1:17:00 JD if things get physical they have to seperate 
1:18:53 AH says she doesn't have the funds for a hotel
1:23:50 AH complains that its JDs house not theirs 
1:33:18 AH repeats what Dr Kipper said to her in a therapy session 
1:37:15 AH says she would do anything to trade places with JD 
1:38:10 Toronto
 1:49:10 AH says she loves JD more than herself 
1:59:45 AH promises she will not resort to the same old behaviour
